name: Seolhyun from AOA
description:
Seolhyun from AOA, 2nd go at LORA training. Going down the list of those I find attractive. Currently uses only 10 pictures as a basis and will experiment with adding more pictures later on, etc.

*Had to use Seolhyun as a trigger word. res 512x768.

Pop on by if you like so far: https://ko-fi.com/volatis
